Title: Mylife Pura X Blood Glucos Monitoring System Glucometer(Black)
Description: Blood glucose meters can be quite different in their design and technology, but also in their performance. Signal transmission from the test strip to the device is crucial for the quality of measurement results. The shorter the transmission path is and the better the signal can be transmitted, the more precise the result of the measurement will turn out to be. mylife Pura and mylife Pura X use the innovative High Definition Signal Transmission (HDST) technology, which makes precise and accurate signaling possible. The very short signal path of just 2.5 mm and gold electrodes minimize interferences and thus ensure the best possible signal transmission. With its innovative HDST technology, mylife Pura offers very low interference, making it one the most accurate blood glucose meters in its class (according to studies made in 2009 and 2013).² ³ Even if the acceptance criteria of the new ISO 15197:2013 are applied, mylife Pura delivers excellent measurement accuracy.

Title: Wild Stone Juice Deodorant Spray  -  For Men(150 ml)
Description: After you’ve played all through the afternoon in the tiring sun, you go home to a cold glass of mango juice and feel replenished. Even now when you return home late after that last minute meeting, completely drained you reach out for that chilling nectar to relax you. Instantly perking up the burned-out man, Wild Stone Juice Deo Spray gives him that extra boost. When you are bogged down by the stress of working hard or your pig-headed boss looking through you, this boost is a much needed spray of confidence. After a spritz of this juice deo spray, you hold your head higher and each step is more firm than the last. You can make your way to confront all those problems and grab what you deserve. This fragrance comes in a scratch-patterned structure that is coloured with a black hue and violet sheen. A smart tux along with a spray of juice from Wild Stone gives you the fortitude to make your day.

Title: Ralph Lauren Big Pony 1 Deodorant Spray  -  For Men(200 ml)
Description: Saddle up to enjoy an exciting day ahead with this Big Pony 1 deodorant spray from Ralph Lauren. Made for the sporty and lively man, this refreshing fragrance features citrusy and fruity notes. This cheerful scent will compliment your fun-loving and go-getter personality. A Sporty Fragrance The reviving body spray features a unique blend of lime and grapefruit notes. This sporty fragrance will instantly energize your senses and leave you smelling great for a long time.

Title: Ralph Lauren Big Pony 3 Deodorant Spray  -  For Men(200 ml)
Description: He finishes the presentation with a flourish and leaves the room that resounds with appreciative applause. His lips pucker as he whistles his favorite tune while he exchanges his formal jacket for a jersey and heads to the tracks to blow off some steam. As he straps himself onto the horse and preps the pony, the slow pulse of speed and finesse invades his veins and he unties all his earthly ties, one by one, to give himself up to the heavenly high that the sport gives him. He is a man of contrasts; he is equally at ease in a boardroom as he is in the great outdoors. Ralph Lauren Big Pony 3 Deo Spray adorns this man who has found and struck the elusive balance between work and play. The fresh mossy green that beckons you into an intense match of wits is captured within this fresh and invigorating potion. The luxury deodorant spray strikes the sweet spot of your olfactory senses with its spicy concoction; Big Pony 3 infuses you with a wave of hard-hitting notes that awaken you from a fugue state and push you on to greater heights. Presented in a sleek green flacon with the picture of a polo shot adorning it, Ralph Lauren Big Pony 3 Deo Spray is definitely the elixir of the luxuriously balanced.

Title: Secret Temptation Mystery Deodorant Spray  -  For Women(150 ml)
Description: You never know what she really thinks and for a while it might seem like you’re walking on eggshells but that’s the price you pay to be with her. A divine persona, she possesses the perfect poker face with an expression that reveals nothing but a bewildering power over everyone. As she dabs on a bit of Secret Temptation Mystery Deo Spray, you can’t help but wonder what is that intriguing ingredient that makes her so striking. Armed with a sweltering stare and cool temperament, she can bring armies to their knees. A one-of-a-kind deo spray that celebrates this woman who knows her power and its effect on others. Although she seems dominant and ruthless, behind this exterior is the loving warmth of a woman. She loves to make you happy and would continue doing so. Mystery deo spray comes in a dual toned bottle of bright fuchsia and tangy orange that spells a radiant aura. After a spritz of this fragrance there is something about the way she looks at you - a passion, a longing, a temptation.
